VALUES ('a8c6ee25-fcee-416a-924a-07bef09c3718', 'FixMyUI', 'fixmyui', 'Turn product feedback into shipped UI code', 'FixMyUI turns product feedback into shipped UI code directly from staging. Instead of filing tickets and waiting for “next sprint,” PMs and Marketing teams click an element, describe the change, and an AI agent edits the repo, commits to Git, and lets CI/CD deploy it. It stands out with a live widget, Git-native workflow, screenshots/files, team tickets, stats, and auditability, with a high degree of customization and control from the CTO if he wishes to (context, unit tests, branches..)', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/c2f62a27-827d-4705-874b-0b8763ad1b5b.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/Z63ZGX2N4HA4HH?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/Z63ZGX2N4HA4HH?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'code', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 1, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:12.112Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
