VALUES ('a3a27665-117c-424c-bbb5-2433315761a3', 'TradeMind Lite', 'trademind-lite', 'AI trading journal calls out your mistakes in first person', 'TradeMind Lite is an AI-powered trading journal that analyzes screenshots of your trades and identifies behavioral mistakes. Unlike generic journals, it speaks in first person and holding up a mirror to your trading psychology. Just send a screenshot to the Telegram bot, and it confesses your mistakes for you. Track patterns with /stats, history with /history Built by a trader who''s made every and all mistakes in the book. Free during beta (10 analyses/month). Unlimited Pro plan coming soon.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/16e06745-0efe-49d0-bb98-aa69ff3c7908.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/OO3DFU6CARHIIG?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/OO3DFU6CARHIIG?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'writing', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 0, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:12.145Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
