VALUES ('4b8ffd4c-5ab1-439b-b983-c8463efc44e9', 'ToneSwap', 'toneswap', 'Every AI tool writes the same. This one writes like you.', 'Every AI writing tool spits out the same bland output. ToneSwap breaks that pattern. Feed it a few writing samples and it learns your voice. Pick from 9 tones and watch it rewrite your text while keeping you sounding like you. It does more than rewrites. Build stories. Craft LinkedIn posts. Thread out tweets. Repurpose content across formats. Analyze what tone you''re actually using. Work on the web, use the Chrome extension, or drop into the app. Everything syncs.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/ebfd043e-d837-4fd7-b609-14512c1c7539.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/YCIPU3VNYRD2AP?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/YCIPU3VNYRD2AP?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'productivity', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 0, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:12.219Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
