VALUES ('5120723c-ab22-46b4-9fac-50db33b693cc', 'Uptrue', 'uptrue', 'Monitor what matters. Get alerted when it breaks.', 'Most monitoring tools cost too much or do too little. Uptrue is one suite — 24 monitor types covering uptime, SSL, domains, WordPress, and status pages. The differentiators: • AI Visibility — track whether ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, Claude, Mistral, Cohere cite your site. Auto-generates llms.txt. No other monitoring suite does this. • Free WordPress plugin on WP.org — 25+ checks from inside • Two-region down confirmation — no false alarms • Free forever, paid from £1/month', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/198fc80f-8f75-46df-85e9-4a0cc4e5196c.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/6ZTUVVCIDCKNLD?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/6ZTUVVCIDCKNLD?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'code', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'free', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 4, 0, 2, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:29.548Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
