VALUES ('04b4357f-0150-4614-a3a6-5375e3ec1ead', 'urgentry - Drop-in Sentry replacement', 'urgentry-drop-in-sentry-replacement', 'Sentry, minus the bill and the YAML', 'Cut your Sentry bill. Keep every SDK. urgentry is the drop-in: change one DSN, send one event, decide in an afternoon. One binary, SQLite, runs on a $5 VM or your laptop. You get issues, alerts, releases, traces, logs, replays, and dashboards on day one. Outgrow Tiny mode? Split-role on Postgres + NATS + S3 is already in the repo. Try the switch this week. If it doesn''t stick, roll back in five minutes.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/77155d71-2b73-4ed4-9a63-a30f3e81c2cf.svg?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/LV2WPQQVK2WQVP?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/LV2WPQQVK2WQVP?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'code', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 0, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:29.585Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
