VALUES ('97dd8b57-4789-42a7-97d3-bb531805822a', 'Spain-Master Guide', 'spain-master-guide', 'Free Digital Guide: Skip Spain''s Admin & Travel Headaches', 'Spain-Master Guide 是专为在西华人打造的数字路书。提供2026最新西班牙旅游避坑攻略、官方门票预订、NIE办理指南、银行开户及地道餐饮推荐。Why choose us? 1.All-in-One: Consolidates logic from dozens of gov/bank sites to save your time. 2.Beginner Friendly: Even a total stranger can live like a local from Day 1 3.Be Independent: Handle NIE and banking yourself. No more expensive agencies. 4.No Download: PWA technology. Just "Add to Home Screen" to use instantly. 5.Master Spain Guide: One free app for all travel, admin, and dining needs.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/28fc3d0a-ae35-4e4d-9f14-690dd78cfd4e.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/TXZEUZ5GZ75NO4?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/TXZEUZ5GZ75NO4?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'productivity', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 0, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:32.357Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
