VALUES ('69923218-afb3-4cb1-a20f-1b218087a468', '同じ月の下で ', '', '  sanctuary: Moonlight on the water, under the same moon.', '"I built a moon instead of words." "under-the-same-moon" is a minimalist sanctuary designed for those who carry too much. In just one minute, it offers a space of profound silence where moonlight touches the water. We often find ourselves under the same moon as someone we can no longer meet. No matter how much we suppress our feelings, they remain. This app isn’t about "doing" something; it’s about "being" there. for those who usually don''t rely on apps but need a moment to breathe.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/d29eeb6b-f42e-4715-ac2d-3d298c63b7a5.png?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/KODG7UDVBM3BAR?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/KODG7UDVBM3BAR?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'design', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 1, 0, 0, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:39:35.135Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
