VALUES ('708362ac-271a-48cd-aa7d-d8711ec92172', 'Audioraq', 'audioraq', 'AI podcast creation studio for serious creators', 'Most people do not stop podcasting because they lack ideas. They stop because production is fragmented. Audioraq gives podcasters an AI production team. A podcaster can answer guided questions, generate an episode package, and pass it through quality review before publishing. So the goal is not more AI content, the goal is to publish podcast quality. Audioraq helps creators start from an idea, create a better episode, publish it into a real show, and learn from listeners.', 'https://ph-files.imgix.net/328efdb4-bf9f-4197-a90a-b5fd3dac758a.jpeg?auto=format', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/2TO73Y43MMBUYQ?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'https://www.producthunt.com/r/2TO73Y43MMBUYQ?utm_campaign=producthunt-api&utm_medium=api-v2&utm_source=Application%3A+Novex+Hunt+ai+%28ID%3A+278703%29', 'productivity', ARRAY['new','product-hunt','free','africa-friendly']::text[], 'freemium', ARRAY[]::text[], TRUE, TRUE, '6.50', 1, FALSE, FALSE, TRUE, FALSE, 'active', 2, 0, 1, '2026-05-12T00:00:00.000Z', '2026-05-12T01:40:01.242Z', NULL, NULL, 'manual', NULL)
