**Fireflies AI** records and transcribes every user call automatically. Your entire product discovery becomes searchable.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620712943543-bcc4688e7485?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620712943543-bcc4688e7485?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'Ship faster, market smarter, support better — the exact tools top founders use to run lean SaaS businesses.', 'The AI Stack Every SaaS Founder Needs in 2026', 'Ship faster, market smarter, support better — the exact tools top founders use to run lean SaaS businesses.', '9384b700-0e32-4db1-b82b-a045130116c3', '53476e71-920c-4697-86ac-250e38d10954', 'published', '2026-04-29T00:16:39.580Z', '2026-05-11T23:59:11.784Z', 8, 110, 611, 25, ARRAY['saas','founder','startup']::text[], TRUE, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-05-11T23:59:11.784Z', NULL, NULL)
