VALUES ('f561cb3a-cd85-4036-a9ed-35b471956c61', 'cursor-vs-copilot-2026', 'Cursor vs GitHub Copilot: Which AI Coding Tool Wins in 2026?', 'We tested both for 30 days on real projects. Here''s the honest verdict.', '## Cursor vs GitHub Copilot: Honest Verdict After 30 Days

### What Cursor Does Differently
Cursor understands your entire codebase. Multi-file edits happen with one natural language command.

### Where GitHub Copilot Wins
Copilot lives inside VS Code — your existing IDE. Zero setup friction. Copilot''s inline completions are also faster.

### The Verdict
**Use Cursor if:** You do full-stack development, work across multiple files, or are a solo founder.

