VALUES ('9dbf78e2-5daa-46d8-ace3-5c4680ddbf22', 'zapier-vs-make-2026', 'Zapier vs Make in 2026: The Honest Comparison', 'After testing both on real client workflows, here''s which automation tool to pick and when.', '## Zapier vs Make: Stop Guessing, Start Automating

### Zapier: The Safe Choice
**Who it''s for:** Non-technical users, small teams, anyone who wants automation ''just to work.''

Zapier''s 7000+ app library is unmatched. The interface is clean.

### Make: The Power User''s Choice
**Who it''s for:** Agencies, developers, operations teams with complex requirements.

Make''s visual flow builder shows you exactly how data moves through your automation.

Cost is Make''s superpower: 10K operations/month for $9.

### n8n: The Third Option
If you can self-host, n8n is worth serious consideration. Free forever, 400+ integrations, and AI nodes.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550751827-4bd374c3f58b?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'After testing both on real client workflows, here''s which automation tool to pick and when.', 'Zapier vs Make in 2026: The Honest Comparison', 'After testing both on real client workflows, here''s which automation tool to pick and when.', '2929c58e-5d2e-4034-a46b-f677c978034a', '9b54b039-f093-4414-83e7-32acdbe33454', 'published', '2026-05-02T16:34:46.085Z', '2026-05-11T23:59:11.796Z', 9, 95, 3015, 25, ARRAY['automation','zapier','make']::text[], FALSE, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-05-11T23:59:11.796Z', NULL, NULL)
