VALUES ('b7d1f784-a4b9-44a8-a371-695fcba20b68', 'midjourney-v7-review', 'Midjourney V7 Review: Is It Worth Upgrading?', 'After 30 days with Midjourney V7, here''s our honest verdict on what changed and whether it matters.', '## Midjourney V7: 30-Day Verdict

### What Actually Changed
**Draft Mode** is the headline feature. Generate a rough image in 8 seconds, iterate, then upscale when you''ve nailed the composition.

**Personalization** works better now. After training on 50 reference images, V7 generates closer to your aesthetic.

**Text in images** is dramatically improved. V7 handles short text with ~85% accuracy.

### V6 vs V7 Quality
Honest take: V7 wins on realism and photography. V6 wins on artistic abstraction.

**Bottom line:** Upgrade. The Draft Mode alone justifies it for professional users.', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510915228919-c4e975ebcef7?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1510915228919-c4e975ebcef7?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'After 30 days with Midjourney V7, here''s our honest verdict on what changed and whether it matters.', 'Midjourney V7 Review: Is It Worth Upgrading?', 'After 30 days with Midjourney V7, here''s our honest verdict on what changed and whether it matters.', '76ffbbd9-bf3b-4639-b16e-83c2dd6afbb6', '53476e71-920c-4697-86ac-250e38d10954', 'published', '2026-04-29T07:45:15.079Z', '2026-05-11T23:59:11.803Z', 7, 89, 4481, 388, ARRAY['design','midjourney','image-generation']::text[], FALSE, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-05-11T23:59:11.803Z', NULL, NULL)
