VALUES ('d65c9001-eb56-42f0-87aa-9c5ff094b106', 'stack-builder-guide-agencies', 'How Top Agencies Build AI Tool Stacks for Clients', 'The methodology behind building AI stacks that solve real problems — not just impressive tool lists.', '## Building AI Stacks That Actually Work

Most ''AI tool stacks'' are just lists. The best ones are engineered workflows where each tool solves a specific problem.

### The Stack Design Methodology
**Step 1: Map the Pain** — Document exactly where time and money are being lost.

**Step 2: Identify the Output Format** — Every tool needs to output in a format the next tool can consume.

**Step 3: Start With One Workflow** — Pick the single workflow that costs the most time or money.

### The Agency Content Stack (Tested)
1. **ChatGPT** → Research brief and outline
2. **Claude** → First draft from outline
3. **Surfer SEO** → Optimization scoring
4. **Grammarly** → Quality check
5. **Canva** → Social graphics from content
6. **Zapier** → Publish to all channels

Time to produce one SEO article: 45 minutes (down from 8 hours).', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?w=1200&h=630&fit=crop&auto=format', 'The methodology behind building AI stacks that solve real problems — not just impressive tool lists.', 'How Top Agencies Build AI Tool Stacks for Clients', 'The methodology behind building AI stacks that solve real problems — not just impressive tool lists.', '9384b700-0e32-4db1-b82b-a045130116c3', 'b37a2332-1fcf-46c2-bf17-4dd4e7d6df93', 'published', '2026-05-03T09:15:14.190Z', '2026-05-11T23:59:11.805Z', 11, 142, 1791, 349, ARRAY['agencies','stack-builder','workflow']::text[], FALSE, FALSE, FALSE, '2026-05-11T23:59:11.805Z', NULL, NULL)
